CSSConfigLogMsgPayload¶

struct CSSConfigLogMsgPayload¶
#include <CSSConfigLogMsgPayload.h>

CSS configuration message log message.

This message is the outpout of each CSS device to log all the configuration and measurement states.

Public Members

[m] sensor position vector in the spacecraft, “B”, body frame

[rad] field of view (boresight to edge)
